    <item>
      <title>随着美国退款启动，全球债券反弹面临供应考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/global-bond-rally-faces-supply-test-as-us-refunding-kicks-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国降息的希望引发的全球债券上涨将在周二面临首次重大考验，财政部本周将开始出售总额达 1,250 亿美元的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/global-bond-rally-faces-supply-test-as-us-refunding-kicks-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 10:01:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与债券持有人达成债务协议后，标准普尔将阿德勒的评级下调了两个档次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/s-p-cuts-adler-by-two-notches-after-debt-accord-with-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在陷入困境的房东与债券持有人签署了一份关于重组债务的非约束性协议后，标准普尔全球评级将阿德勒集团的评级从“CCC+”下调至“CCC-”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/s-p-cuts-adler-by-two-notches-after-debt-accord-with-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 10:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行对可能降息的疑虑加剧：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/riksbank-suspense-mounts-over-possible-rate-cut-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行要么本周要么削减借贷成本以提振经济，要么放弃避免克朗贬值的举措，这是多年来最令人悬念的决定之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/riksbank-suspense-mounts-over-possible-rate-cut-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
