      <title>澳大利亚丰益糖厂因工资问题面临停工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/wilmar-sugar-mills-in-australia-face-industrial-action-over-pay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位工会官员表示，丰益国际有限公司旗下的澳大利亚糖厂占该国一半以上的产量，因要求加薪而面临罢工行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/wilmar-sugar-mills-in-australia-face-industrial-action-over-pay</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
